===Pronunciation===

:feld spayth' oid

===Etymology===

:Feld, field (from Middle High German veld, from Old High German feld) + Spath, spar + Oid, like or resembling.

===Noun===
#A small group of [[igneous]], [[plutonic]], and [[volcanic]] [[mineral]]s formed in [[magma]] that did not contain enough [[silica]] to satisfy all the chemical bonds. Feldspathoids are  silica-poor variants of the [[feldspar]] group.


